javax.ws.rs.ext
Interface ResourceInfo

public interface ResourceInfo

An injectable class to access the resource class and resource method matched by the current request. Methods in this class MAY return null if a resource class and method have not been matched. E.g., in a PreMatchRequestFilter.

Since:
2.0
Author:
Santiago Pericas-Geertsen
